title: Selling Sunset: Davina Intervention
description:
The video version of this recap is up as part of Crappens on Demand http://bit.ly/crappensvideo on Patreon
Davina has a lot of negativity coming her way in the Selling Sunset office, but she's got a huge house to sell before she can worry about it.
For this week's premium bonus about catching up on TV and podcasts, become a member over at Patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens.
